### Create POST API Route Handler - App Router

Source: https://context7.com/vercel/next.js/llms.txt

Implements a POST endpoint in App Router that sets an HTTP cookie using NextResponse. Uses the cookies() function from next/headers to access the cookie store and demonstrates basic response handling with JSON data.

```typescript
// app/api/set-token/route.ts
import { NextResponse } from 'next/server';
import { cookies } from 'next/headers';

export async function POST() {
  const cookieStore = await cookies();
  const res = NextResponse.json({ message: 'successful' });
  res.cookies.set('token', 'this is a token');
  return res;
}
```

